caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

 shows the polynomial 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

 on the left side and the convergence graph of the approximation error on the right side.
 We observe the expected convergence to machine precision at 
\begin_inset Formula $n=26$
\end_inset

 nodes/weights,
