\begin_inset Formula $C(I)$
\end_inset


\family default
\series default
\shape default
\size default
\emph default
\nospellcheck default
\bar default
\strikeout default
\xout default
\uuline default
\uwave default
\noun default
\color inherit
 with respect to the 
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}$
\end_inset

-norm:
\family roman
\series medium
