 itself,
 closed under complements and countable unions).
 A function 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu:\varSigma\rightarrow\left\langle 0,\infty\right\rangle $
\end_inset

 is called a measure on the measurable space 
\family roman
\series medium
\shape up
\size normal
