\begin_layout Plain Layout

\end_layout

\end_inset

The accuracy of the approximated eigenpairs 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\tilde{\lambda}_{i},\tilde{u}_{i}\right)$
\end_inset

 obtained from the Galerkin method can be quantified by examining the residual error.
 This residual measures how closely the approximate solution satisfies the original integral eigenvalue problem 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:eigenproblem"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

.
 The magnitude of this error is typically measured using the 
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}$
\end_inset

-norm of the residual function 
\begin_inset Formula $R_{i}(x)=\intop_{\mathcal{T}}c\left(x,y\right)\tilde{u}_{i}\left(y\right)\,dy-\tilde{\lambda}_{i}\tilde{u}_{i}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

,
 defined as:
 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\Vert R_{i}\right\Vert _{L^{2}}=\left\Vert \intop_{\mathcal{T}}c\left(x,y\right)\tilde{u}_{i}\left(y\right)\,dy-\tilde{\lambda}_{i}\tilde{u}_{i}\left(x\right)\right\Vert _{L^{2}}=\left(\intop_{\mathcal{T}}\left(\intop_{\mathcal{T}}c\left(x,y\right)\tilde{u}_{i}\left(y\right)\,dy-\tilde{\lambda}_{i}\tilde{u}_{i}\left(x\right)\right)^{2}dx\right)^{1/2}.
\]

\end_inset

In Figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:Residuum-of-eigenpairs"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

,
 we see the residual for the first five approximate eigenpairs as the number of basis polynomials,
 and therefore the size of matrix 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

,
 increases.
 We observe that the residual decreases substantially only for either the even- or odd-indexed eigenpairs at each step,
 in an alternating fashion.
 This is because the basis polynomials being added alternate between even and odd degrees,
 and adding a polynomial of a certain parity primarily refines the approximations of the eigenpairs with the corresponding parity.
 
\begin_inset Float figure
placement document
alignment document
wide false
sideways false
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Graphics
	filename Graphs/EigenpairsResiduum.pdf

\end_inset


\end_layout

